        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Helping Expand Access to Rural Telemedicine Act of 2017 or the HEART Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill provides for Medicare coverage of: (1) additional telehealth services, and (2) remote patient-monitoring services for certain chronic conditions.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
